{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01K88z6ihPGsAUjGDkbpYb3w","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All three images are now available in the kind cluster. Now let me proceed with the upgrade.\n\nThe plan:\n1. Update ConfigMap to remove deprecated `queue_master_locator = min-masters` setting\n2. Scale down to 0\n3. Change image to 3.12-management\n4. Scale up to 3\n5. Wait for cluster to be healthy\n6. Enable all feature flags on 3.12\n7. Scale down to 0\n8. Change image to 4.1-management\n9. Scale up to 3\n10. Verify\nI'm realizing there's a version constraint I need to account for—the official upgrade path from 3.12 to 4.1 actually requires going through 3.13 and 4.0 first, since 4.0 specifically requires 3.13 as the minimum version. However, if I do a full shutdown between versions, there might be some flexibility here.\n\nThe real question is whether 4.1 can directly read and migrate the Mnesia data from 3.12 without those intermediate steps. Since 3.12 uses Mnesia for metadata, 4.0 introduced Khepri as an alternative but still supported Mnesia, and 4.1 continues to support Mnesia-based clusters, the data format itself should be compatible. The concern is whether specific migration steps from 3.13 or 4.0 need to have already run before 4.1 can process the data. For a simple cluster without quorum queues or streams, this might actually be workable.\n\nBefore attempting the upgrade, I should update the ConfigMap to remove deprecated settings like `queue_master_locator = min-masters`, which could cause startup failures in 4.1.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":209,"cache_read_input_tokens":52008,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":209},"output_tokens":22,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ec4bed2d-f2eb-45a6-8f17-10f0087f0ba3","uuid":"e37ec1bd-842a-4906-8598-64d234c24fb9","request_id":"req_011CcRLxbkb3stEkDN1aj8LY"}
